🚀 Exciting News! We are thrilled to announce the release of our latest work:“Vec-QMDP: Vectorized POMDP Planning on CPUs for Real-Time Autonomous Driving.” Vec-QMDP redefines real-time planning by leveraging CPU-native SIMD parallelism to achieve over 200x speedup, delivering millisecond-level decision-making for large-scale autonomous driving.
